Bad Clustering Example ⚠️

Real Example Query

SELECT SUM(revenue)
FROM fact_sales
WHERE order_date BETWEEN '2026-01-01' AND '2026-01-31'
AND customer_id = 101;

Partitioning:

reduces scanned partitions


Clustering:

reduces scanned blocks inside partition


Together = powerful optimization.


